high_descs: Turn toward the fridge and turn right and go towards the kitchen sink
Pick up the green apple out of the sink
Turn around and walk towards the microwave with the apple and open the microwave door
Put the apple in the  microwave and close the door and turn it on for a few seconds, then open the door and take the apple out
Turn around and walk back to the sink
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Get an apple from the sink and heat it up in the microwave

high_descs: Turn left, go straight, turn right into kitchen.
Pick up apple in the sink.
Place apple into microwave, close microwave.
Cook apple in microwave, open microwave, grab apple.
Turn around towards sink, throw apple into sink.
anns.task_desc: Cook apple in microwave, place in sink.

high_descs: Turn to the left, then to the right, then to the sink on the right.
Pick up the apple, to the left of the egg.
Turn around and go to the microwave in front of you.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Return to the sink behind you.
Put the apple in the sink, to the right of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple in the sink.
